{"id": "22903", "post": "<div class=\"post-22903 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-dark-theme tag-lowendbox tag-lowendtalk tag-new-feature tag-related-posts\" id=\"post-22903\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/new-feature-related-posts-on-lowendbox-making-it-easier-than-ever-to-find-cheap-vps-deals/\" rel=\"bookmark\">New Feature: Related Posts on LowEndBox \u2013 Making it easier than ever to find Cheap VPS Deals!</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/dark-theme/\" rel=\"tag\">dark theme</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/lowendbox/\" rel=\"tag\">lowendbox</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/lowendtalk/\" rel=\"tag\">lowendtalk</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/new-feature/\" rel=\"tag\">new feature</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/related-posts/\" rel=\"tag\">related posts</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> June 1, 2020 @ 7:31 am, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTY5IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE2OSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/leb-banner-300x169.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\"></a></p><p>Over the last few weeks we have been busy working to make improvements to LowEndBox and LowEndTalk. In late April, thanks to the great efforts of <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/profile/FAT32\">@FAT32</a> we implemented a <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/164234/dark-theme-is-here\">dark theme on LowEndTalk</a>, along with many other improvements and features (<a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/164108/vanilla-upgrade\">vanilla forum software upgrade</a>, <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/163999/text-editor-issue\">better text editor</a>, <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/164105/bug-reports-feature-requests\">and a lot more</a>).</p><p>Today we are announcing the implementation of \u201cRelated Posts\u201d on LowEndBox. This new feature utilizes software/machine learning to match up related posts with one another with the goal of helping our users find exactly what they are looking for easier and with more options \u2013 inexpensive VPS, web hosting, dedicated servers, and more.</p><p>Please let us know in the comments if you have any trouble with the new feature.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI3MTAiIGhlaWdodD0iNTU2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzEwIDU1NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-22904\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/RelatedPosts-2.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"710\" height=\"556\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/RelatedPosts-2.jpg.webp 993w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/RelatedPosts-2-300x235.jpg.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/RelatedPosts-2-768x602.jpg.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\"></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-t